reviewText: The Product was okay. I expected btter music and quality, too much self promotion.

Ruben Blades y  Juan Luis  Guerra  demuestran que son los mejores artistas de su generacin. Yo  no  soy amante de la msica de Robi  as  que  me  encontr  saltando esa seccin. En  realidad no es de la altura de  Rubn y  Juan  Luis  Guerra.

I enjoyed each artist, their background, music and their countries.  I love music from Puerto Rico They have such good diversity of rhytms and what can you say about Ruben Blades from Panama he is an amazing singer composer honestly a genius  the same goes for the poetry of Jusn Luis Guerra. Loved it!!!!
THIS IS ONE OF MY PRICED DVD'S . THERE ARE PARTS WITH EACH OF THESE ARTIST TALKING ABOUT THE MUSIC,PEOPLE,CULTURE, AND CUBA. ALL THREE END UP PUTTING AN UNFORGETTABLE CONCERT.
Esto me dio mucho trabajo conseguirlo. Esta caro, pero realmente vale la pena. Excelente sonido.
